OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 27 APR
OL,4,CTELETEXT
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1985FTeletext subtitles have a new
OL,7,Fhome on all UK terrestrial channels:
OL,8,Fpage 888.
OL,9,
OL,10,FThis new standardised number would also
OL,11,Fbe used by new TV channels thereafter.
OL,12,
OL,13,FPreviously, teletext subtitles were
OL,14,Favailable on the following pages:
OL,15,F- BBC One: Ceefax page 170.
OL,16,F- BBC Two: Ceefax page 270.
OL,17,F- ITV: ORACLE page 170.
OL,18,F- Channel 4: ORACLE page 470.
